  MapEntry(15, "{\"page\":15,\"total_results\":300,\"total_pages\":15,\"results\":[{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613740,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Montreux Jazz Festival 2013 - Remember Claude Nobs\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/rL5vRD8tqxVcVHzXYVvdbKRcG4H.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"it\",\"original_title\":\"Montreux Jazz Festival 2013 - Remember Claude Nobs\",\"genre_ids\":[10402],\"backdrop_path\":\"\\/7AqVcESmAeh8jgfkCNBxZwMhAG7.jpg\",\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-12\"},{\"vote_count\":1,\"id\":613742,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":9,\"title\":\"NJPW G1 Climax 29, Day 1\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/NJMJsnDX66THIQid1ZTDpwofms.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"NJPW G1 Climax 29, Day 1\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":\"\\/4mrsvLOkGEWxUUQoVIBnUzkVYPo.jpg\",\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"The opening night of the 29th edition of the G1 Classic, headlined by Hiroshi Tanahashi vs. Kazuchika Okada in Dallas, Texas.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-06\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":608914,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"With a Breath.\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/AcYjxPuQJo0E7maiOFRhbNEfR4c.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"With a Breath.\",\"genre_ids\":[99],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Documentary following a first-time filmmaker on a 3-year journey making a film on VHS, The Forgotten Colours of Dreams.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-03\"},{\"vote_count\":1,\"id\":613644,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":7,\"title\":\"Echoes of Departure\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/e5ujMVoe7U9k1khI066aiFycPzU.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Echoes of Departure\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Two office workers meet between moments of banality. The newest film by Hon Hoang starring Jennifer Khoe and Monica Cho.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-05\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613802,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"XY\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":null,\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"XY\",\"genre_ids\":[99],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Different young men. Different questions. Different perceptions about women. And the force of habit.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-08\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613804,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Schroot\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":null,\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Schroot\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Geert Van Steenkiste, also known as The Photo Radar Marathon Man (a billing agent), likes his car so much, a Nissan Micra, that he doesn\'t want to get rid of it. When a repurchase man arrives to take away his car, he tries to convince not to take it to the car crusher. Failing his attempt, the situation takes on other proportions.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-08\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613806,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Direito à Memória\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":null,\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Direito à Memória\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"From an unpublished audio recording of a rally from general Humberto Delgado held at a Chaves cine-theater, on May 22, 1958, in the midst of an election campaign that would determine his assassination by PIDE\'s fascist forces, Rúben Sevivas rehearses a pertinent manifesto for the right to memory, both the figure of the \\\"General without fear\\\" and, in a more personal register, the Cine-Parque de Chaves, the flavian cine-theater where the rally was held and which is now deactivated.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-08\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613808,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Estas Mãos São Minhas\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":null,\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Estas Mãos São Minhas\",\"genre_ids\":[99,18],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"In the form of a photo-novel, in which a succession of static images construct a narrative with the support of the voice-over, \\\"Estas Mãos São Minhas\\\" is a love letter of André Miguel Ferreira to his grandmother. The pretext is one of the usual trips of Sundays and Thursdays of the grandmother, with the most elegant clothes and the best perfume, to dance sessions where, in this space of music and conviviality, married men hide their alliances and widowed women search for ghosts. And it is a particular ghost that really matters to the young director, his deceased grandfather, for whom his grandmother cries silently and for whom sometimes he changes his name. This is a film about the loss, the longing, the time, the fear, the love and the immense strength of women.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-08\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613809,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Há Alguém na Terra\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":null,\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Há Alguém na Terra\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"In a bucolic place on the island of Flores, the most remote of the Azores archipelago, a lonely man lives in complete isolation, without any kind of human interaction. To keep you company, just a black cat and a spotted cow. His daily routine is lived between his house and a lighthouse that apparently is, or has been, in his charge. Produced by Francisca Magalhães, Joana Tato Borges and Maria Canela, \\\"Há Alguém na Terra\\\" is a film about the passage of time, about someone who seems to be saying goodbye to life and its routines. Told without recourse to any kind of dialogue, the film lives on a particular visual and sound ambience, which invites the viewer to contemplate.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-08\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613810,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Berço\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":null,\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Berço\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"The title cradle refers to a house, more properly a boat house, where the main characters of this story live. Anchored in a small marina, the three - a mother, the father and a teenage son - try to manage the small occurrences of a routine different from the usual in a different life. The relationship between the mother and her child is disturbed when a group in a neighbouring boat invites the child to join a small party and the child glimpses a piece of freedom. Through a sensuous look, reflected in the time that the film devotes to the small gestures, this is a melancholy bump over the passage of time and about growth.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-08\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613844,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Desolate\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/2XTkQwYeBHVYdNlaQcEY0e49xt9.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Desolate\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"While trying to survive the worst drought in history, a family of farmers force their youngest brother down a path of destruction; betrayed and left for dead in an unfamiliar land, he must survive, endure and seek the revenge he deserves.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-12\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613846,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"The Miracles of Jeane\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/aNbpzHnqyNAovfwgiciQXCPXClF.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"The Miracles of Jeane\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"The story of a man, Joe, who loves the current life he has, regardless of the unhappiness it brings him, as a mysterious person enters his life, and makes him question everything. Joe is presented the opportunity to gain happiness and save his soul, but in order to do so, he must leave his old life and everything he loves behind him.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-03\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":570427,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Qué tal Pascual\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/3iihQ1DKm5R7i1J8El1r6TvYi7X.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"es\",\"original_title\":\"Qué tal Pascual\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Pascual Iranzo is an enigmatic hairdresser from Barcelona with a unique idea of what it means to cut hair. Who is this special man who seems to be something straight out of a hall of wonders? At 87, Pascual has maintained his supreme hairdressing skills and boasts incredible vitality. There’s no doubt about how much Pascual defies normality with his singular way of understanding the world. Between scissors, friends and cocktails, Pascual elegantly shows us what an eccentric, unique and irreplaceable person he is, a man who never ceases to transform and reinvent himself.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-01\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":546261,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"The Guest\",\"popularity\":1.4,\"poster_path\":\"\\/zJWyLLrDg9Ch2thpvcU1kqkyCcD.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"it\",\"original_title\":\"L\'ospite\",\"genre_ids\":[35,18],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Dumped by his girlfriend and finding himself stranded on different couches at friends’ places, Guido tries to transform his drift into an opportunity for a new beginning.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-10\"},{\"vote_count\":1,\"id\":613851,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":7,\"title\":\"Anna: The Woman Who Went to Fight ISIS\",\"popularity\":0.6,\"poster_path\":\"\\/s41COyYMoeBKb5XfywcTVMSXR07.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Anna: The Woman Who Went to Fight ISIS\",\"genre_ids\":[99],\"backdrop_path\":\"\\/8Pedc3ah68UPYlILYHNKGK4UpOr.jpg\",\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"In 2017, 25-year-old Anna Campbell from Lewes in East Sussex travelled in secret to northern Syria. She was heading for Rojava, the Kurdish territory in the north of the country. In the midst of the civil war in Syria, a fledgling feminist democracy had been established but almost immediately came under threat from the so-called Islamic State. Just eight months after arriving and with no military background, Anna went to the front line to fight with Kurdish YPJ. A month later she was killed by a Turkish air strike. With access to her diary and videos filmed while she was there, this film explores what motivated Anna to leave and how her family make sense of the tragic consequences.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-07-01\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613322,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Sermon on the Mount\",\"popularity\":0.6,\"poster_path\":\"\\/gwk8MU4zjCCqjo5xeyjyK8kil6B.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Sermon on the Mount\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Jerrod Carmichael explores aspects of the black experience through interviews with his family in this HBO Special.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-06-30\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613877,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Family Pictures\",\"popularity\":0,\"poster_path\":\"\\/bwZQ5RUIP9Oi3dBXa5jaLr73FwL.jpg\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Family Pictures\",\"genre_ids\":[],\"backdrop_path\":null,\"adult\":false,\"overview\":\"Sylvie and Maggie are strangers living on opposite coasts, leading very similar lives with husbands that travel for work too much and daughters about to leave the nest. But when their daughters befriend each other on a college tour, they soon discover a shocking secret that threatens to tear both families apart.\",\"release_date\":\"2019-06-29\"},{\"vote_count\":0,\"id\":613936,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":0,\"title\":\"Il trovatore - Teatro Real\",\"popularity\":0,\"poster_path\":\"\\/tO1fsDZYsp9h8zuzjjO4WoAXbva.jpg\",\"original_language\":